Yeah, so just a few introductory words, introductory slides to set the stage for what we are doing

01:29.000 --> 01:31.560
today.

01:31.560 --> 01:36.960
We already showed you we are coming from train companies, and we met basically in an initiative

01:36.960 --> 01:40.080
to create an open rail foundation.

01:40.080 --> 01:46.760
