02:04.680 --> 02:06.640
You see the URL on the slide.

02:06.640 --> 02:08.280
There's some more information.

02:08.280 --> 02:12.440
The idea is to really spread open source in the railway, and that's where we all personally

02:12.440 --> 02:17.640
stand behind and what we want to spread, and hopefully some of you who are related to this

02:17.640 --> 02:23.800
topic as well join us in this effort.

02:23.800 --> 02:29.480
While we are doing that, of course, the core of that is the openness, being open, doing

02:29.480 --> 02:30.640
open source software.

02:30.640 --> 02:31.840
That's why we are all here.

02:31.840 --> 02:35.960
That's why an event like Fostem is happening.

02:35.960 --> 02:39.360
For us, it's a little bit more than just the open source license.

02:39.360 --> 02:44.480
