02:44.480 --> 02:49.000
For the Open Rail Foundation specifically, of course, the goal is to enable open collaboration

02:49.000 --> 02:51.640
in the railway sector.

02:51.640 --> 02:57.560
But we don't want to stop at railways, and that's also because transport is more than

02:57.560 --> 02:59.920
